---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | AskDaveDowntown"
  description="Privacy policy for AskDaveDowntown - how we collect, use, and protect your personal data."
  noindex={true}
>
  <Section>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-ink">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-ink-muted text-sm">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you contact Dave via WhatsApp or email, you share your contact details voluntarily. We do not collect personal data through this website automatically beyond standard server logs.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>Your contact details are used solely to respond to your enquiry. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties.</p>

      <h2>Cookies and Analytics</h2>
      <p>This site is a static website and does not use tracking cookies. It uses Google Fonts, which may set cookies as part of font delivery.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>This site uses Google Fonts for typography. External links to WhatsApp, Instagram, and LinkedIn are governed by those platforms' own privacy policies.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal data we hold. Contact Dave directly at dave.buckley@paragonproperties.ae.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? Email dave.buckley@paragonproperties.ae.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</PageLayout>
